      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUIRKY CHARACTER (9) is in terrific form with five wins a second from his last six starts. Took his record at this circuit and distance to three from four when coming from this row to score by 1.2m last start. Can do it again. KYVALLEY MAVEN (6) has chased QUIRKY CHARACTER home when runner-up in his last two starts but did beat that rival when winning easily here last month. Could turn the tables on him again. HILLTOP HUGH (1) makes his first appearance since his Group 1 Vicbred Super Series win here four months ago. Progressive trotter who gets the ace draw and has been readied with a series of trials. EL RESAMO (8) came from a wide barrier to place behind QUIRKY CHARACTER last start and draws for a trail. RUBYS DREAM (2) has put together a series of top-two finishes and is up to a distance where she strikes at 50 per cent. Draws to be competitive again.",
